data.description: Welcome to charming 167 W Shevlin Ave! Meticulously maintained and cared for home throughout all the years. Located on a T-street which brings less traffic!   If you go North-South-East-West you will be sure to hit all the major freeways in no time at all. Hopping downtown Hazel Park has many community activities, bike lanes, many local go to restaurants, shopping and just down the avenue from Ferndale, Royal Oak bustling areas.  Lets get to the bones! Large living room featuring a ton of natural light. Kitchen with in-room dining area with immense  storage, laundry room/mud room and utility room all in one spot! Three great size bedrooms allowing space for office, game room, guest bedroom, primary master or whatever your heart desires!   Natural paint! - Move right in!  Location and care is what this one is all about! DO NOT MISS!
